{"tid":2176174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"奧巴馬政府營救的維權人士陳光誠，都支持侵侵","createTime":"2020-08-27T02:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T13:45:49.000Z","uid":48040,"like":135,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd803fe5e7d30879ff547b8916af7e150b556fe","tid":2176174,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"盲人律師陳光誠2012年進入美國大使館尋求庇護，並在2012年5月2日在美國駐華大使駱家輝陪同下離開大使館，到達北京市朝陽醫院。後經奧馬巴政府及中國政府談判，陳與家人成功離開中國，抵達美國紐約，在紐約大學擔任訪問學者。<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">當年陳光誠獲救，與奧巴馬政府有莫大關係。但陳光誠今天出席了共和黨大會，轉而支持特朗普。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking-news/section/6/153986/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandard.com.hk%2Fbreaking-news%2Fsection%2F6%2F153986%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=fd54c067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking-news/section/6/153986/</a>(Republican-Convention)-Dissident-Chen-Guangcheng-says-Chinese-Communist-Party-is-enemy-of-humanity<br />\n<br />\n救命之恩還救命之恩，陳光誠清楚，要救千千萬萬同胞，靠民主黨死得，都係支持共和黨更好。<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n加入我們YouTube <br />\n一齊探討關於抗爭的哲學！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Un_cMz6bad8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUn_cMz6bad8&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9f2b71f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Un_cMz6bad8</a>"},{"pid":"f4623041ccb7d5de6cf3f34ab951ee7d15ae6315","tid":2176174,"uid":48040,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kb67cXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkb67cXW.png&h=d3950cae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d3d4ee564a7e47a69e14215bdfcfbb651343cf2","tid":2176174,"uid":186071,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"2012年 維尼 未正式掌權 <br />\n有鬼佬照真係走得出中國 中共都唔想煩<br />\n<br />\n今時今日除時死多兩錢重<img src=\"/assets/face